  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>A set of cartilage pincers nip softly at the inside of the egg.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">dutiful</span> nature, happiest when assigned useful tasks.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>一对软腭正在蛋壳里轻柔开合。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">尽职</span>的基因潜质，最喜欢被指派做有用的工作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>一對軟骨組成的鉗子輕輕夾了蛋殼內部一下。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">責任心重</span>天性，指派有用的差事給牠，就會覺得很開心。"
  },
